==================================================

* Bugs fixed:
 328997 64bit pointer trunction in glib slab-allocator
        [Pascal Hofstee]
 331110 g_cond_broadcast(inform_cond) without holding 
        inform_mutex [Chris Wilson, Sebastian Wilhelmi]
 332093 Fix some leaks in the tests [Kjartan Maraas]
